{"lemma":"نَحْبُ","slug":"نَحْبُ","root":"ن.ح.ب","root_slug":"ن-ح-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ح-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"نَحْب","root":"نحب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":0},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n39465","","n39468"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n39465","headword_ar":"نَحَبَ","root":"nHb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHobN","text_ar":"نَحْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, A, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nH~b","text_ar":"نحّب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tanoHiybN","text_ar":"تَنْحِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He vowed; made a vow;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put himself under an obligation to do a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHaba","text_ar":"نَحَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHobN","text_ar":"نَحْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He laid a bet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wager; betted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wagered."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) [The explanation of the inf. n. by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muraAhanapN","text_ar":"مُرَاهَنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the K, seems to imply that it is the same as 3; but this appears to be doubtful.]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHaba","text_ar":"نَحَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHiybN","text_ar":"نَحِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) or this is a subst., (Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHobN","text_ar":"نَحْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AntHb","text_ar":"انتحب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He raised his voice with weeping,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wailing; wept,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wailed, loud;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wept,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wailed, most violently;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wept,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wailed, with prolonged voice."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHaba","text_ar":"نَحَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuHaAbN","text_ar":"نُحَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHobN","text_ar":"نَحْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel, S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had a cough,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coughed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S K.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHaba","text_ar":"نَحَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHobN","text_ar":"نَحْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went, travelled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journeyed, at a quick pace:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a light pace:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with much exertion and perseverance."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [The inf. n. only is mentioned, and said, in the S, to be syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEobN","text_ar":"نَعْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","AA"]},{"entry_id":"n39468","headword_ar":"نَحْبٌ","root":"nHb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A vow."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaDaY naHobahu","text_ar":"قَضَى نَحْبَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He died:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was slain in an expedition undertaken for the sake of God's religion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"originally meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he accomplished his vow:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see Kur, xxxiii. 23: (Msb:) as though he had constrained himself [by a vow] to fight until he died: (TA:) or it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he ended his term,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"period of life; ended his days:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, Zj:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he finished his time:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(as implied in the S): or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he yielded his soul:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he accomplished his want:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] from significations given"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2773},{"kind":"text","text":"below. (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHobN","text_ar":"نَحْبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A great bet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wager:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaTarN EaZiymN","text_ar":"خَطَرٌ عَظِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) So in the following verse of Jereer:"},{"kind":"quote","text":"biTixofapa jaAladonaA Almuluwka waxayolunaA\n                      \n                     \n                        Ea$iy~apa bisoTaAmK jarayona EalaY naHobi"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In Tikhfeh we contended with the sword with the kings; and our horses, in the evening of Bistám, ran for a great bet"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHobN","text_ar":"نَحْبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A proof; a demonstration; an evidence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"burohaAnN","text_ar":"بُرْهَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A necessity; want; needful thing; an object of want"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"need:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAjapN","text_ar":"حَاجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaDaY","text_ar":"قَضَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHobahu","text_ar":"نَحْبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b6-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Death."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaDaY naHobahu","text_ar":"قَضَى نَحْبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", above. ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A term; fixed period;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"period of life."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaDaY naHobahu","text_ar":"قَضَى نَحْبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", above. ―         -b8-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soul:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafosN","text_ar":"نَفْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (AO, K.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mind; purpose; aspiration; desire; ambition:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"him~apN","text_ar":"هِمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ximosN naHobN","text_ar":"خِمْسٌ نَحْبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A laborious journey:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAy^ibN","text_ar":"دَايِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sayorN","text_ar":"سَيْرٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHobN","text_ar":"نَحْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"syr munaH~ibN","text_ar":"سير مُنَحِّبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A quick pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journey."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b3-  The same epithets are likewise applied, in the same sense, to a man. (TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHobN","text_ar":"نَحْبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A quick"},{"kind":"text","text":"(or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"light,"},{"kind":"text","text":"K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mode of going, travelling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journeying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with much exertion and perseverance."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAra fulaAnN EalaY naHobK","text_ar":"سَارَ فُلَانٌ عَلَى نَحْبٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one went on, travelled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journeyed, with energy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for a great bet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wager;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] as though he had laid a [great] bet, and therefore strove, or exerted himself. (S.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHobN","text_ar":"نَحْبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Length."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, K.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ywm","text_ar":"يوم"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nHb","text_ar":"نحب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[so in the TA: perhaps,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomu naHobK","text_ar":"يَوْمُ نَحْبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but more probably"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomN naHobN","text_ar":"يَوْمٌ نَحْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A long day."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Riyáshee.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHobN","text_ar":"نَحْبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A space of time: a time."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaDaY naHobahu","text_ar":"قَضَى نَحْبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", above. ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sleep:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nawomN","text_ar":"نَوْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L, K: in some copies of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomN","text_ar":"يَوْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"TA.) ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fatness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b11-  I. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$id~apN","text_ar":"شِدَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Vehemence; violence; &c.:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distress; difficulty; adversity; &c."},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) ―         -b12-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A game of hazard:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qimaArN","text_ar":"قِمَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)       -A3-  A"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"great"},{"kind":"text","text":"camel. (K.) Perhaps a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najobN","text_ar":"نَجْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","TA","Fr","Zj","K","AA","S"]}]}}